  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK554">
<l>kūḻum kuṭiyu moruṅkiḻakkuṅ kōlkōṭic </l>
<l>cūḻātu ceyyu maracu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king, who, without reflecting (on its evil consequences), perverts justice, will lose at once both his wealth and his subjects.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
